00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,600
Did you know tool use isn't just for humans?

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:05,600
Chimpanzees are our closest relatives.

3
00:00:05,600 --> 00:00:08,000
They fish for termites using sticks.

4
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,000
This behavior reveals their deep understanding of cause and effect.

5
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,400
Research shows chimps select the right tools, adjusting them for efficiency.

6
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:17,200
Amazing, right?

7
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:22,800
This suggests a level of cognitive complexity that we once thought was uniquely human.

